hffm_solution

This is the base class of solution objects. Initially, solutions (derived types that is) will encapsulate some simple functionality:

1) copying a solution (essentially deep copy)
2) freeing a solution
3) varying a solution
4) measuring the error on a solution


random number generators

hffm_rand_load("mersenne twister");
hffm_rand_default_seed(); // read time, read dev random, entropy, internet
hffm_rand_small_seed(long seed);

size_t hffm_rand_seed_len();
void hffm_rand_seed(char *seed);


uint32_t hffm_rand_uint32()

